<div class="info-box">
  <h4>Which Method Is Right for You?</h4>
  <p>
    <strong>Hot weather or sensitive stomach:</strong> Cold Brew — low acid, smooth, and convenient to batch-prepare<br />
    <strong>Love espresso-style intensity without a machine:</strong> Moka Pot — compact, affordable, produces bold concentrated coffee<br />
    <strong>Interested in cultural tradition and ritual:</strong> Ibrik — the oldest living brewing tradition, deeply tied to social ceremony<br /><br />
    All three have low entry costs and offer a completely different perspective on coffee compared to pour over or espresso. A V60, a Moka Pot, and a cold brew jar in your kit covers an extraordinary range of coffee experiences.
  </p>
</div>

